Hania handles the administrative tasks, but also looks after the children if all hands on deck are required.
The youngest employee of the daycare. Xenia loves playing with the kids and reading them stories and she is clearly the favorite of most of the kids.

Lara is the owner of the Daycare. She is a woman in her mid to late 40s and always seems to carry a slightly stern expression. Once one gets to know her better, she reveals herself to be a very caring and hard working woman who takes quite a bit of joy and pride in her job.
The Silver Dragons serve and protect the people, acting as the first line of defense against would-be villains and criminals.

The Mages are a small but well-trained unit within the Kingdom of Kohlingen. The symbol of Mystra emblazoned on their cloaks, they work diligently as a branch of the Silver Dragons, under the command of the Magister.
